Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, it was so many flowers that they wouldn't\Neven fit in the dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, it was brand name clothes and bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the biggest jewels I've ever seen in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea who was sending them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt something special when I first saw your show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or my ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you can't see with your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have come to the dressing\Nroom to meet me in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you seem like you might actually listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:31.30,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(238,200)\pos(366,347)}The Baby's Depression
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had anything so good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always eat food like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But depending on one's dining companions,\Nthe meal can taste either good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually eat alone, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you usually eat with a group of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I pay many people to come dine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how many people\NI invite, or how lively it gets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always feel like I'm eating alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you dine with me like this from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I'll get tired of eating food like this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have been strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I built my kingdom here in Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fought to create a new order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream was to be like General Hitler...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to become a dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm doing now is a little different, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone's eyes are glued to me when I dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so good when I dance, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never felt like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the three murders that took\Nplace over the last few months...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Johan's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand the meaning behind the murder of\NFritz Overt from the Bilker Investment Bank...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the daughter of the general\Nstore owner, Frieder Schelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scandal cover-ups...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were aware of these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The foreign trader, Erich Klemperer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably unrelated to Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really know what Johan's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you hiding something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have you located Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After leaving the psychiatrist's home in Munich...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it appears she came here to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't securing Nina our top priority?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you're aware of Nina's true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget that she's Johan's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the night of the burning of the Turkish district...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes, as she pointed the gun at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:06:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gives me chills just thinking of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about the program you created?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was merely assisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is proceeding according to my master's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going according to\Nthe program he has created.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are things really proceeding according to the program?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best ice cream in Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt this relaxed in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been so stressed lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to put so many bodyguards around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Mr. {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek has ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I go for a walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there aren't many people who would recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there would be more trouble if we\Nlet you do whatever you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's doing as he pleases?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three people have died to cover up your scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can kill as many people\Nas I want and not get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think gave you your current power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The four leaders of the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor G{\fnMeiryo U}ö{\fnNarkisim}derich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your late father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to think that you've succeeded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, things aren't that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is whether or not you\Nare worthy of that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that you're meant to take that position?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all the scandals that surround you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should also know what happens\Nto those who know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a long way to go before you\Ncan even think about threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never dream of making you my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a leader of Frankfurt's extreme right wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I asked you out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask me out any time you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I enjoyed walking around\Ntown without a bodyguard like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to walk you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that you'll protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hotel is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live in a hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my usual habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bought people with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To your hotel room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls you "The Baby," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what's your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've located the twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just called The Baby, but he isn't answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going directly to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.08,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The Baby has...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.59,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,The Baby has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.40,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.40,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.40,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mr. {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, please forgive my rude question, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you weren't the one who killed The Baby, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a ridiculous question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,news of The Baby's death will have spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the death of The Baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the balance of the organization\Nwill be completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no idea how things will turn out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will carry out the jobs given to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you were the one who killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then protecting you will be a farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I ordered you two to protect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:14:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,immediately after I heard about The Baby's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you felt something was\Ngoing to happen to you next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an idea about who killed The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:14.89,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we really know what Johan's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,proceeding according to the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll move you somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a small house in Idstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told anyone about that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay there for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, the twin sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you found out where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here in Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a cheap hotel called the Tourette.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Securing that girl will be the best guarantee\Nof my safety right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tomorrow morning, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a call to have two other guards\Nprotect you at your house in Idstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, The Baby sent his bodyguards\Nhome for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He acted by himself, and that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have us with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were also saved from the assassination attempt\Nthe other day at the convention center.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very lucky person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.75,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.46,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Milan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.75,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:10.26,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I met a wonderful person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Peter {\fnMeiryo U}Č{\fnNarkisim}apek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You showed me something truly wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me more about your readings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know about your completely new...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should read these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is drawn in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such beautiful children!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These children are the ones who will\Nbecome the leaders of tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,according to your program. Right, Franz Bonaparta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your house is just up ahead, over this mountain road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be two other bodyguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a chance those two would\Nleak the information to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guarantee that the information\Nabout me going to my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hasn't been leaked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both very trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case, we're not going to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pointless to keep driving at night like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your life is in danger, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for now, let's head to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't going for his gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone... here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people drank that red wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I'm drinking it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bodyguards that were supposed to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill The Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to be on the same side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to look for your sister and bring her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already located her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your sister will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go the way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, everything is going according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster I thought was inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Franz Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.95,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,471)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:44.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:44.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.34,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:23:01.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:23:01.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:25.88,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:34.30,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.76,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
